# Built oom-watch binaries
oom-watch/oomwatch
oom-watch/oommemhog

# Generated tarballs
oom-toolkit-*.tar.gz

# Diagnostic log files produced by `make oomwatch-diagnose`. The script
# writes to /tmp/ by design, but if a contributor copies a log into the
# repo for review (or a future script change emits one here) we don't
# want it tracked. The log can contain hostnames, journal extracts, and
# process names from the user's actual machine — not appropriate for VCS.
oomwatch-diagnose-*.log
*.diagnose.log

# Editor / OS noise
*.swp
.DS_Store
